  "keyFeatures": [
    "Cross-platform game launcher for Linux",
    "Automatic Wine and DXVK installation and management",
    "Telemetry disabling for privacy protection",
    "Multi-language support (20+ languages)",
    "Game update and voice pack management",
    "Multiple launcher styles (Modern and Classic)",
    "Predownload support for game updates",
    "Session management for multiple game instances"
